3BA%20lot%20of%20hybrid%20electric%20vehicles%20now%20are%20not%20far%20off%20from%20their%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20alternatives.%20So%20I%20think%20that%20the%20lower%20incremental%20costs%20associated%20with%20hybrids%20at%20this%20point%20are%20driving%20some%20interest%20towards%20hybrid%20versus%20fully%20electric%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299ed0829-d858-4969-b375-e264f3970cfd%5C%22%3ESoaring%20gas%20prices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESinger%20said%20that%20gas%20prices%2C%20which%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eia.gov%2Fdnav%2Fpet%2Fhist%2FLeafHandler.ashx%3Fn%3Dpet%26s%3Demm_epm0_pte_nus_dpg%26f%3Dm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremained%20high%20since%20the%20pandemic%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20could%20also%20be%20having%20an%20impact%20on%20consumers'%20decision%20to%20opt%20for%20more%20fuel-efficient%20vehicles%20versus%20gas%20versions.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20seen%20historically%20is%20that%20when%20gas%20prices%20rise%2C%20hybrid%20electric%20vehicle%20price%20or%20acquisitions%20rise%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20we%20came%20out%20of%20the%20pandemic%20period%2C%20gas%20prices%20have%20seen%20an%20increase%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20probably%20a%20significant%20reason%20why%20hybrid%20electric%20vehicles%20have%20grown%20in%20popularity%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cc0e6a0-dfd4-4147-bf9a-040ac5319f05%5C%22%3ECharging%20hurdles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20big%20winners%20of%20the%20latest%20hybrid%20craze%20is%20Toyota%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoyota-hybrid-cars-ev-sales-growth-prius-bz4x-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20skeptical%20approach%20to%20EVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20many%20of%20its%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20carmaker%20beat%