ist%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20sent%20to%20AFP%20by%20de%20Robertis%2C%20one%20woman%20tagged%20Courbet's%20work%20with%20red%20paint%20and%20then%20a%20second%20sprays%20another.%20They%20then%20chant%20%26quot%3BMeToo%26quot%3B%20before%20being%20dragged%20away%20by%20security%20guards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20open%20letter%2C%20de%20Robertis%20denounced%20the%20behaviour%20of%20six%20men%20in%20the%20art%20world%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bpredators%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcensors%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDe%20Robertis%20said%20they%20had%20also%20seized%20an%20embroidery%20work%20by%20French%20artist%20Annette%20Messager%20as%20%26quot%3Breappropriation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecutor%20said%20a%20third%20person%20--%20who%20was%20not%20arrested%20--%20could%20have%20been%20behind%20the%20disappearance%20of%20the%201991%20Messager%20work%20titled%20%26quot%3BI%20Think%20Therefore%20I%20Suck%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDe%20Robertis%20has%20a%20work%20on%20display%20at%20the%20venue%20in%20Metz%20--%20a%20photograph%20of%20a%202014%20performance%20at%20the%20Musee%20d'Orsay%20in%20which%20she%20posed%20naked%20underneath%20Courbet's%20painting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20French%20court%20in%202020%20ordered%20de%20Robertis%20to%20pay%20a%202%2C000-euro%20(%242%2C150)%20fine%20for%20appearing%20naked%20in%202018%20in%20Lourdes%20in%20southwest%20France%2C%20a%20Catholic%20pilgrimage%20site%20for%20those%20who%20believe%20the%20Virgin%20Mary%20appeared%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20also%20shown%20herself%20naked%20in%20front%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMona%20Lisa%26quot%3B%20painting%20at%20the%20Louvre%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715397420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2