%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fearthquake-of-magnitude-4-5-strikes-afghanistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F110025063.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fearthquake-of-magnitude-4-5-strikes-afghanistan%2Famp_articleshow%2F110025063.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20Successfully%20Tests%203D-Printed%20Rocket%20Engine%20-%20A%20Major%20Breakthrough%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%20successfully%20conducted%20a%20long-duration%20test%20of%20its%20PS4%20engine%2C%20re-designed%20for%20production%20using%20cutting-edge%20additive%20manufacturing%20(AM)%20techniques%20--%20also%20known%20in%20common%20parlance%20as%203D%20printing%20--%20and%20crafted%20in%20Indian%20industry%2C%20the%20space%20agency%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20engine%2C%20now%20a%20single%20piece%2C%20saves%2097%20per%20cent%20of%20raw%20materials%20and%20reduces%20production%20time%20by%2060%20per%20cent%2C%20ISRO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20achieved%20the%20major%20milestone%20with%20the%20successful%20hot%20testing%20of%20a%20liquid%20rocket%20engine%20manufactured%20through%20AM%20technology%20for%20a%20duration%20of%20665%20seconds%20on%20May%209%2C%20a%20release%20from%20the%20space%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engine%20used%20is%20the%20PS4%20engine%20of%20PSLV%20(Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle)%20upper%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDesign%20%26amp%3B%20Manufacturing%20Breakthrough%3A%3Cbr%3E%5CnISRO%20successfully%20conducts%20a%20long-duration%20test%20of%20the%20PS4%20engine%2C%20re-designed%20for%20production%20using%20cutting-edge%20additive%20manufacturing%20techniques%20and%20crafted%20in%20the%20Indian%20industry.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20new%20engine%2C%20now%20a%20single%20piece%2C%20saves%2097%25%20of%20raw%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYdDsDm3YGF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYdDsDm3YGF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1788891338299289683%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PS4%20engine%20manufactured%20in%20the%20conventional%20machining%20and%20welding%20route%20has%20been%20in%20use%20for%20the%20fourth%20stage%20of%20PSLV%20which%20has%20a%20thrust%20of%207.33%20kN%20in%20vacuum%20condition.%20The%20same%20engine%20is%20also%20used%20in%20the%20Reaction%20Control%20System%20(RCS)%20of%20the%20first%20stage%20(PS1)%20of%20PSLV%2C%20the%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engine%20uses%20the%20earth-storable%20bipropellant%20combinations%20of%20Nitrogen%20Tetroxide%20as%20oxidiser%20and%20Mono%20Methyl%20Hydrazine%20as%20fuel%20in%20pressure-fed%20mode.%20It%20was%20developed%20by%20ISRO's%20Liquid%20Propulsion%20Systems%20Centre%20(LPSC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELPSC%20redesigned%20the%20engine%20making%20it%20amenable%20to%20the%20Design%20for%20Additive%20Manufacturing%20(DfAM)%20concept%20thereby%20gaining%20considerable%20advantages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Laser%20Powder%20Bed%20Fusion%20technique%20employed%20has%20brought%20down%20the%20number%20of%20parts%20from%2014%20to%20a%20single-piece%2C%20and%20eliminated%2019%20weld%20joints%2C%20saving%20significantly%20on%20the%20raw%20material%20usage%20per%20engine%20(13.7%20kg%20of%20metal%20powder%20compared%20to%20the%20565%20kg%20of%20forgings%20and%20sheets%20for%20conventional%20manufacturing%20process)%20and%20reduced%2060%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20overall%20production%20time%2C%20the%20ISRO%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20engine%20was%20done%20in%20Indian%20industry%20(M%2Fs%20WIPRO%203D)%2C%20and%20the%20engine%20was%20hot%20tested%20at%20ISRO%20Propulsion%20Complex%2C%20Mahendragiri%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20development%20programme%2C%20the%20injector%20head%20of%20the%20engine%20was%20realised%20and%20successfully%20hot%20tested%20earlier.%20Detailed%20flow%20and%20thermal%20modelling%2C%20structural%20simulation%2C%20and%20cold%20flow%20characterisation%20of%20the%20proto%20hardware%20were%20carried%20out%20to%20gain%20confidence%20for%20the%20hot%20test%2C%20ISRO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20four%20successful%20developmental%20hot%20tests%20of%20integrated%20engine%20were%20conducted%20for%20a%20cumulative%20duration%20of%2074%20seconds%20which%20validated%20the%20engine%20performance%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20engine%20was%20successfully%20tested%20for%20the%20full%20qualification%20duration%20of%20665%20seconds%20and%20observed%20that%20all%20the%20performance%20parameters%20were%20as%20expected.%20It%20is%20planned%20to%20induct%20this%20AM%20PS4%20engine%20into%20the%20regular%20PSLV%20programme%2C%20ISRO%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715392500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ft37lhqb4_isro-ps4-rocket-engine-tested-successfully_625x300_11_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-successfully-tests-3d-printed-rocket-engine-a-major-breakthrough-5637114%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ISRO%20has%20successfully%20conducted%20a%20long-duration%20test%20of%20its%20PS4%20engine%2C%20re-designed%20for%20production%20using%20cutting-edge%20additive%20manufacturing%20(AM)%20techniques%20--%20also%20known%20in%20common%20parlance%20as%203D%20printing%20--%20and%20crafted%20in%20Indian%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-successfully-tests-3d-printed-rocket-engine-a-major-breakthrough-5637114%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-successfully-tests-3d-printed-rocket-engine-a-major-breakthrough-5637114%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-successfully-tests-3d-printed-rocket-engine-a-major-breakthrough-5637114%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Fair%20For...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ganguly's%20Clear%20Take%20On%20KL%20Rahul-Sanjiv%20Goenka%20Saga%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20captain%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20on%20Friday%20said%20the%20Indian%20team%20management%20should%20make%20Virat%20Kohli%20open%20in%20next%20month's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20to%20exploit%20the%20star%20batter's%20rich%20vein%20of%20form%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20Kohli%20is%20the%20current%20Orange%20Cap%20holder%20in%20this%20IPL%20with%20634%20runs%20from%2012%20matches%2C%20averaging%2070.44%20and%20at%20an%20impressive%20strike-rate%20of%20153.51%2C%20which%20is%20significantly%20higher%20than%20his%20career%20rate%20of%20134.31.%20%E2%80%9CVirat%20is%20playing%20exceptionally%20well.%20The%20way%20Kohli%20batted%20last%20night%20%E2%80%93%2090%20in%20quick%20time%2C%20you%20need%20to%20use%20him%20as%20opener%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20He%20should%20open%2C%20evidenced%20by%20his%20last%20few%20IPL%20innings%20which%20have%20been%20outstanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganguly%20told%20PTI%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20promotional%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%20said%20India%20have%20picked%20a%20balanced%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20which%20has%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20land%20the%20trophy%20after%20a%20gap%20of%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20lone%20triumph%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20came%20in%202007%2C%20the%20inaugural%20edition%20held%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20excellent%20squad.%20I%20think%20they%20have%20picked%20the%20best%20possible%20squad.%20Apart%20from%20batting%20depth%2C%20bowling%20looks%20excellent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBumrah%20is%20the%20best%20fast%20bowler%20in%20the%20world%20at%20the%20moment.%20We%20have%20experience%20in%20Kuldeep%2C%20Axar%2C%20Siraj.%20It's%20an%20ideal%20combination%20we%20have%20this%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ganguly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20edition%20of%20the%20IPL%20has%20seen%20teams%20breaching%20the%20250-run%20mark%20quite%20effortlessly%2C%20and%20the%2051-year-old%20said%20the%20trend%20would%20continue%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20trend%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%20T20%20cricket%20has%20become%20a%20power-oriented%20game%20and%20that's%20what%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20reading%20Sanju%20Samson's%20comments%20the%20other%20day%2C%20where%20he%20said%20there's%20no%20time%20to%20settle%20down%20in%20modern%20T20s.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20hit%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20way%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ganguly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkatan%2C%20himself%20no%20stranger%20to%20hitting%20some%20monster%20sixes%20during%20his%20playing%20days%2C%20identified%20the%20evolved%20mindset%20of%20batters%20and%20Impact%20Player%20rule%20as%20the%20main%20reasons%20behind%20such%20mammoth%20totals%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20in%20IPL%20we%20are%20seeing%20scores%20like%20240%2C%20250%20regularly.%20The%20main%20reasons%20are%20good%20batting%20wickets%20and%20the%20grounds%20are%20also%20not%20big%20in%20India.%20In%20the%20last%20game%20between%20Delhi%20Capitals%20and%20Rajasthan%20(Royals)%2C%2026%20sixes%20were%20hit%20in%20a%2040-over%20game%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20one%20six%20every%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat's%20how%20this%20game%20has%20gone%20and%20that's%20how%20the%20players%20have%20started%20approaching%20the%20game.%20The%20Impact%20Player%20rule%2C%20where%20every%20team%20has%20the%20possibility%20of%20adding%20another%20batsman%2C%20has%20also%20added%20another%20dimension%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20detailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%20said%20the%20bowlers%20need%20to%20upskill%20themselves%20to%20counter%20the%20ruthless%20march%20of%20batters%20in%20T20s%2C%20and%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20pacer%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20general%20ruins%20of%20bowlers%2C%20Bumrah%20stood%20tall%2C%20grabbing%2018%20wickets%20from%2012%20matches%20and%20his%20economy%20rate%20of%206.20%20is%20the%20best%20among%20regular%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bowlers%20need%20to%20be%20really%20more%20skillful%2C%20we%20have%20some%20skillful%20bowlers%20around%2C%20to%20be%20more%20successful.%20Look%20at%20Bumrah%2C%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20all%20of%20them%20bowl%20superbly%20in%20all%20formats%20of%20the%20game%20and%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don't%20believe%20in%20formats.%20I%20believe%20in%20skills.%20These%20are%20exemplary%20players%20who%20will%20thrive%20in%20all%20formats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20he%20think%20the%20power-hitting%20will%20take%20the%20elegance%20and%20artistry%20away%2C%20making%20cricket%20robotic%3F%20%E2%80%9CNot%20at%20all.%20Demands%20of%20different%20formats%20are%20different.%20Everything%20evolves%2C%20sports%20is%20not%20an%20exception.%20You%20will%20still%20see%20elegance%20and%20artistry%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20Test%20matches%20will%20always%20be%20Test%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20quality%20players%20will%20be%20successful%20in%20all%20formats%20of%20the%20game.%20Look%20at%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%A6the%20best%20players%20will%20adjust%20to%20all%20formats%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20had%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20return%20to%20the%20Indian%20side%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20but%20Ganguly%20said%20the%20selectors%20made%20the%20right%20choice%20by%20selecting%20Rishabh%20Pant%20and%20Sanju%20Samson%20as%20wicketkeeper%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDinesh%20played%20well%20but%20there%20are%20better%20players%20than%20Dinesh.%20I%20don't%20think%20you%20can%20leave%20Sanju%20or%20Rishabh%20out.%20There%20are%20better%20players%20than%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20at%20the%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ganguly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanguly%20also%20refrained%20from%20commenting%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20reprimand%E2%80%9D%20given%20to%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20by%20the%20team%20owner%20Sanjiv%20Goenka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20fair%20for%20me%20to%20make%20a%20comment%20based%20on%20a%20TV%20grab.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20Sanjeev%20had%20spoken%20to%20Rahul.%20So%2C%20I%20leave%20it%20at%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715392140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fg2d3s8g8_kl-rahul_625x300_09_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fnot-fair-for-me-sourav-gangulys-clear-take-on-kl-rahul-sanjiv-goenka-saga-5632092%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sourav%20Ganguly%20refrained%20from%20commenting%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20reprimand%26quot%3B%20given%20to%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20by%20the%20team%20owner%20Sanjiv%20Goenka.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20William%20Shares%20A%20Rare%20Update%20On%20Wife%20Kate%20Middleton's%20Health%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBritain's%20Prince%20William%20said%20on%20Friday%20his%20wife%20Kate%20Middleton%20was%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20well%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20r