22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fkga31cuo_ms-dhoni_625x300_11_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Ffan-invades-pitch-to-touch-ms-dhonis-feet-what-happens-next-watch-5635875%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fan%20invaded%20the%20pitch%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%20to%20touch%20MS%20Dhoni's%20feet%20during%20the%20IPL%202024%20match%20between%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20and%20Gujarat%20Titans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Strides%20In%20Arctic%2C%20Antarctica%2C%20Himalayas%20To%20Be%20Taught%20In%20Schools%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20strides%20in%20research%20on%20the%20Arctic%2C%20Antarctica%20and%20the%20Himalayas%20may%20soon%20figure%20in%20school%20textbooks%2C%20with%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20NCERT%20to%20include%20the%20latest%20developments%20in%20its%20curriculum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinistry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20Secretary%20M%20Ravichandran%20said%20the%20National%20Council%20for%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%20has%20constituted%20a%20committee%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20importance%20of%20research%20in%20these%20areas%20in%20school%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20them...%20they%20(NCERT)%20have%20recently%20constituted%20a%20committee%20for%20bringing%20out%20importance%20of%20the%20Antarctica%20expedition%2C%20Arctic%20and%20also%20the%20Himalayas%20and%20some%20other%20aspects%2C%20including%20climate%20change.%20They%20are%20working%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ravichandran%20said%20during%20an%20interaction%20with%20PTI%20editors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Antarctica%20expedition%20finds%20mention%20in%20NCERT%20textbooks%20but%20the%20content%20hasn't%20been%20updated%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20There%20is%20very%20limited%20mention%20of%20the%20ongoing%20research%20in%20the%20Arctic%20and%20the%20Himalayan%20regions%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rationalisation%20exercise%20post%20COVID-19%2C%20the%20NCERT%20dropped%20topics%20such%20as%20climate%20change%2C%20monsoon%20and%20greenhouse%20effect%20from%20textbooks%2C%20triggering%20a%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20later%20clarified%20that%20the%20subjects%20had%20been%20dropped%20to%20reduce%20curriculum%20load%20in%20view%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20added%20that%20the%20topics%20would%20be%20restored%20with%20the%20release%20of%20books%20based%20on%20the%20new%20curriculum%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20books%20are%20currently%20being%20worked%20on%20and%20will%20be%20available%20for%20all%20classes%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20is%20hosting%20the%2046th%20meeting%20of%20the%20ATCM%2C%20the%20highest%20governing%20body%20for%20Antarctica%2C%20and%20the%2026th%20CEP%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crucial%20meets%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Kochi%20from%20May%2020-30%20where%20countries%20engaged%20in%20research%20in%20the%20southern%20polar%20region%20will%20share%20the%20outcome%20of%20their%20scientific%20pursuits%20and%20future%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20two%20active%20research%20stations%20--%20Maitri%20and%20Bharti%20--%20in%20Antarctica.%20The%20first%20research%20station%2C%20Dakshin%20Gangotri%2C%20set%20up%20in%201983%2C%20had%20to%20be%20abandoned%20after%20it%20sank%20in%20the%20snow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThamban%20Meloth%2C%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Polar%20and%20Ocean%20Research%20(NCPOR)%2C%20said%20several%20students%20involved%20in%20the%20research%20have%20been%20to%20Antarctica%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20taken%20any%20high%20school%20students%20so%20far%20but%20several%20senior%20students%20involved%20in%20the%20research%20have%20been%20to%20Antarctica%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20possibilities%20of%20introducing%20a%20programme%20such%20as%20Students%20on%20Ice%20for%20Indian%20school%20students%2C%20Meloth%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20logistically%20feasible.%20It%20costs%20around%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20send%20a%20single%20person%20to%20Antarctica...%20there%20are%20lot%20of%20other%20logistical%20issues%20too%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20high%20school%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Students%20on%20Ice%20programme%20is%20run%20by%20Canadian%20educator%20and%20environmentalist%20Geoff%20Green%2C%20under%20which%20high%20school%20students%20from%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20accompanied%20by%20educators%20and%20scientists%2C%20get%20an%20opportunity%20travel%20to%20Antarctica%20and%20the%20Arctic.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715391360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F7hfafnlg_indias-bharati-research-station-in-antarctica_625x300_10_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-strides-in-arctic-antarctica-himalayas-to-soon-be-taught-in-schools-5630592%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20strides%20in%20research%20on%20the%20Arctic%2C%20Antarctica%20and%20the%20Himalayas%20may%20soon%20figure%20in%20school%20textbooks%2C%20with%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20NCERT%20to%20include%20the%20latest%20developments%20in%20its%20curriculum.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-strides-in-arctic-antarctica-himalayas-to-soon-be-taught-in-schools-5630592%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject