CMEs)%20--%20expulsions%20of%20plasma%20and%20magnetic%20fields%20from%20the%20Sun%20--%20came%20just%20after%201600%20GMT%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%20(NOAA)'s%20Space%20Weather%20Prediction%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20later%20upgraded%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bextreme%26quot%3B%20geomagnetic%20storm%20--%20the%20first%20since%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BHalloween%20Storms%26quot%3B%20of%20October%202003%20caused%20blackouts%20in%20Sweden%20and%20damaged%20power%20infrastructure%20in%20South%20Africa.%20More%20CMEs%20are%20expected%20to%20pummel%20the%20planet%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20lit%20up%20with%20people%20posting%20pictures%20of%20auroras%20from%20northern%20Europe%20and%20Australasia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20just%20woken%20the%20kids%20to%20go%20watch%20the%20Northern%20Lights%20in%20the%20back%20garden!%20Clearly%20visible%20with%20the%20naked%20eye%2C%26quot%3B%20Iain%20Mansfield%2C%20a%20think%20tanker%20in%20Hertford%2C%20Britain%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbsolutely%20biblical%20skies%20in%20Tasmania%20at%204am%20this%20morning.%20I'm%20leaving%20today%20and%20knew%20I%20could%20not%20pass%20up%20this%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20photographer%20Sean%20O'%20Riordan%20posted%20on%20X%20alongside%20a%20photo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20notified%20satellite%20operators%2C%20airlines%20and%20the%20power%20grid%20to%20take%20precautionary%20steps%20for%20potential%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20changes%20to%20Earth's%20magnetic%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20solar%20flares%2C%20which%20travel%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20light%20and%20reach%20Earth%20in%20around%20eight%20minutes%2C%20CMEs%20travel%20at%20a%20more%20sedate%20pace%2C%20with%20officials%20putting%20the%20current%20average%20at%20800%20kilometers%20(500%20miles)%20per%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20emanated%20from%20a%20massive%20sunspot%20cluster%20that%20is%2017%20times%20wider%20than%20our%20planet.%20The%20Sun%20is%20approaching%20the%20peak%20of%20an%2011-year%20cycle%20that%20brings%20heightened%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Go%20outside%20tonight%20and%20look'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMathew%20Owens%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20space%20physics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Reading%2C%20told%20AFP%20that%20while%20the%20effects%20would%20be%20largely%20felt%20over%20the%20planet's%20northern%20and%20southern%20latitudes%2C%20how%20far%20they%20would%20extend%20would%20depend%20on%20the%20storm's%20final%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGo%20outside%20tonight%20and%20look%20would%20be%20my%20advice%20because%20if%20you%20see%20the%20aurora%2C%20it's%20quite%20a%20spectacular%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20If%20people%20have%20eclipse%20glasses%2C%20they%20can%20also%20look%20for%20the%20sunspot%20cluster%20during%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20this%20could%20include%20places%20such%20as%20Northern%20California%20and%20Alabama%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENOAA's%20Brent%20Gordon%20encouraged%20the%20public%20to%20try%20to%20capture%20the%20night%20sky%20with%20phone%20cameras%20even%20if%20they%20can't%20see%20auroras%20with%20their%20naked%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20go%20out%20your%20back%20door%20and%20take%20a%20picture%20with%20the%20newer%20cell%20phones%20and%20you'd%20be%20amazed%20at%20what%20you%20see%20in%20that%20picture%20versus%20what%20you%20see%20with%20your%20eyes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Spacecraft%20and%20pigeons%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFluctuating%20magnetic%20fields%20associated%20with%20geomagnetic%20storms%20induce%20currents%20in%20long%20wires%2C%20including%20power%20lines%2C%20which%20can%20potentially%20lead%20to%20blackouts.%20Long%20pipelines%20can%20also%20become%20electrified%2C%20leading%20to%20engineering%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpacecraft%