.%20I%20believe%20in%20memorializing%20people%20by%20keeping%20them%20alive%20in%20your%20heart%2C%20memories%2C%20actions%20and%20thoughts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa8847b0-3fff-40d8-b062-ca4840344f86%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20see%20her%20everywhere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20mother%20continues%20to%20be%20with%20me.%20I%20often%20have%20conversations%20with%20her%20in%20my%20head.%20I%20share%20stories%20that%20she'd%20find%20funny.%20Or%20I%20tell%20her%20about%20deals%20I%20got.%20We%20both%20loved%20bargains%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsephora-workers-say-hours-cut-free-makeup-perks-ending-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efreebies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20see%20my%20mom%20everywhere%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20look%20in%20the%20mirror.%20Everyone%20says%20I%20resemble%20her%20with%20my%20high%20cheekbones%20and%20light-colored%20eyes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20been%20rummaging%20through%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorced-mom-used-poshmark-to-rebuild-closet-with-tight-budget-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclosets%20and%20drawers%20for%20items%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20save%20to%20keep%20her%20close.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20pins%20and%20necklaces%20she%20made%20from%20broken%20watches%20and%20other%20found%20objects%2C%20including%20ping-pong%20balls%20covered%20in%20subway%20maps%20that%20became%20pop-art%20beads.%20Or%20fun%20patterned%20clothing%20she%20wore%20because%20my%20dad%20liked%20her%20in%20bright%20colors.%20And%20purses%20galore%2C%20including%20a%20quirky%20one%20shaped%20like%20a%20chicken.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeed%20a%20missing%20button%3F%20She%20had%20hundreds%20to%20choose%20from.%20She%20upgraded%20most%20of%20her%20clothing%20with%20her%20