%3E%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20nations%20have%20introduced%20a%20host%20of%20sanctions%20targeting%20Russian%20goods%2C%20including%20bans%20on%20Russian%20energy%20flows%20and%20a%20%2460%20price%20cap%20on%20Russian%20oil%20traded%20using%20Western%20shipping%20and%20insurance%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20measures%20have%20helped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-sanctions-russian-trade-banking-financing-ruble-ukraine-war-funding-2024-5%5C%22%3Ecrimp%20Moscow's%20war%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they've%20likely%20also%20resulted%20in%20higher%20prices%20for%20Western%20consumers%2C%20Rubin%20said.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-youre-still-spending-much-of-your-budget-on-food-2024-2%5C%22%3EFood%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-prices-crude-inventories-fed-rate-cut-outlook-powell-testimony-2024-3%5C%22%3Eenergy%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20soared%20since%20the%20West%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%2C%20he%20noted%20partly%20because%20Russia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20exporters%20of%20oil%20and%20grain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20could%20worsen%20if%20US%20trade%20with%20Russia's%20allies%2C%20like%20China%2C%20becomes%20impacted%2C%20Rubin%20said.%20US%20firms%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20shifting%20their%20operations%20to%20countries%20that%20are%20on%20more%20friendly%20terms%20with%20the%20US%2C%20but%20America's%20closest%20allies%20are%20countries%20where%20workers%20earn%20high%20wages%2C%20which%20can%20push%20prices%20up%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20forced%20a%20crippling%20rise%20in%20interest%20rates%2C%20as%20central%20banks%20such%20as%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Board%20and%20the%20Bank%20of%20Canada%20were%20reluctantly%20forced%20to%20respond%20by%20raising%20their%20target%20interest%20rates%20from%20near%20zero%20to%20the%205-per-cent%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERubin%20notes%20that%20Russia%20had%20quietly%20sanction-proofed%20much%20of%20its%20economy%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20invasion%2C%20while%20the%20BRICS%20bloc%20of%20nations%20expanded%20and%20became%20more%20intertwined.%20This%20helped%20insulate%20Russia%20against%20the%20measures%2C%20and%20rising%20economies%20in%20the%20global%20south%20helped%20Putin%20blunt%20the%20impact%20of%20sanctions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20fatal%20miscalculation.%20Whereas%20in%20the%20past%20the%20loss%20of%20Western%20markets%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20for%20Russian%20energy%20exports%2C%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20Moscow's%20war%20machine%20%E2%80%93%20would%20have%20dealt%20a%20fatal%20blow%20to%20the%20Russian%20economy%2C%20that%20certainly%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20US%20dollar%20may%20end%20up%20worse%20off%20due%20to%20sanctions%2C%20Rubin%20said.%20Russia%20has%20been%20coordinating%20with%20its%20allies%20to%20shift%20away%20from%20using%20the%20US%20dollar%20for%20trade.%20Russia's%20trade%20with%20China%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdedollarization-dollar-dominance-brics-currrency-china-russia-trade-yuan-ruble-2023-12%5C%22%3Ecompletely%20phased%20out%20the%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Russian%20officials%20said%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanctioning%20the%20ruble%20and%20confiscating%20a%20third%20of%20the%20Russian%20central%20bank's%20foreign%20reserves%20was%20supposed%20to%20cripple%20the%20Russian%20economy.%20Instead%2C%20it%20has%20cost%20the%20US%20dollar%20its%20five-decade%20status%20as%20the%20petrocurrency%20of%20the%20world%20and%20may%20soon%20cost%20it%20even%20more%3A%20its%20once%20unrivalled%20position%20as%20the%20sole%20reserve%20currency%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubin%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-russia-sanctions-impact-dedollarization-oil-inflation-war-ukraine-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715370185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e774ab4abc992e8c873f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-russia-sanctions-impact-dedollarization-oil-inflation-war-ukraine-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20may%20have%20opened%20a%20%26quot%3BPandora's%20box%20of%20unintended%20consequences%26quot%3B%20by%20imposing%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%2C%20one%20economist%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-russia-sanctions-impact-dedollarization-oil-inflation-war-ukraine-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mbappe%20announces%20he%20will%20leave%20Paris%20St-Germain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715369575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_sport%2Feb7a%2Flive%2F5c0f70d0-6139-11ee-ac8c-9d18dbc280ea.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fc72pgzvzr23o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22France%20striker%20Kylian%20Mbappe%20says%20he%20will%20leave%20Paris%20St-Germain%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A757%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fc72pgzvzr23o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fc72pgzvzr23o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Farticles%2Fc72pgzvzr23o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bus%20plunges%20off%20bridge%20in%20Ru