0support%20them%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20way%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20expansive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20or%20KCR%20as%20he%20is%20popularly%20known%2C%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%20his%20party%20is%20far%20from%20finished%20and%20will%20get%20seats%20in%20the%20double%20digits%20out%20of%20the%2017%20constituencies%20in%20Telangana.%20He%20also%20answered%20questions%20about%20the%20BJP's%20prospects%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bfailure%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20his%20daughter%20K%20Kavitha%20in%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20for%20sitting%20MP%20and%20one%20of%20the%20candidates%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Nama%20Nageswara%20Rao%2C%20the%20BRS%20chief%20had%20said%20Mr%20Nageswara%20Rao%20could%20end%20up%20being%20a%20Union%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20this%20and%20whether%20he%20would%20support%20the%20NDA%20or%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20KCR%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20tell%20you%20a%20surprising%20thing%20which%20you%20may%20not%20believe.%20This%20time%2C%20something%20new%20is%20going%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20country.%20All%20the%20regional%20parties%20are%20very%20strong%20now.%20They%20will%20emerge%20as%20a%20force.%20It's%20not%20the%20regional%20parties%20supporting%20NDA%20or%20INDIA.%20It's%20nothing%20like%20that.%20Either%20of%20them%20will%20have%20to%20support%20the%20regional%20parties'%20group.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20reverse%20thing.%20You%20will%20see%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao's%20party%20had%20won%20nine%20out%20of%20the%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Telangana%20in%202019%20and%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20since%20its%20formation%20in%202014.%20But%2C%20since%20the%20Congress'%20big%20victory%20in%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20last%20year%20-%20it%20won%2064%20of%20the%20state's%20119%20seats%2C%20securing%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own%20-%20there%20has%20been%20talk%20of%20the%20BRS'%20star%20being%20on%20the%20wane%2C%20which%20has%20been%20reinforced%20by%20several%20leaders%20deserting%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20poser%20on%20this%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20fulfilled%20the%20promises%20it%20had%20made%20in%20the%20six%20months%20it%20has%20been%20in%20power%20and%20people%20are%20angry%20with%20the%20Revanth%20Reddy%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20promise%20they%20have%20delivered%20is%20free%20bus%20(tickets)%20for%20the%20woman.%20Even%20that%20has%20become%20a%20big%20joke.%20Women%20are%20fighting%20in%20the%20buses%20and%20auto%20drivers%20are%20(protesting)%20on%20the%20roads.%20That's%20the%20reason%20people%20are%20very%20angry.%20The%20farming%20community%2C%20which%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20during%20my%20regime%2C%20is%20also%20very%20angry.%20And%20I%20think%20the%20reflection%20will%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20party%20will%20get%20seats%20in%20the%20double%20digits%2C%20going%20up%20to%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20he%20thought%20people%20defeated%20his%20government%20because%20they%20were%20angry%20with%20him%20and%20believed%20the%20parties%20who%20said%20he%20was%20inaccessible%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20replied%20in%20the%20negative%20and%20said%20that%20people%20had%20got%20stable%20supply%20of%20power%2C%20drinking%20water%20and%20water%20for%20irrigation%20under%20his%20government%20and%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Btempted%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Congress'%20promises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20made%20very%2C%20very%20attractive%20promises.%20The%20(vote%20share)%20margin%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20BRS%20was%201.8%25.%20We%20won%20about%20one-third%20seats%20of%20the%20state%20Assembly%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20small%20thing.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20rout...%20It%20was%20a%20small%20thing%20where%20the%20people%2C%20out%20of%20temptation%20and%20because%20they%20believed%20that%20Congress%20may%20deliver%20more%20than%20KCR...%20we%20were%20defeated.%20Now%20everyone%20has%20realised%20the%20Congress%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20and%20has%20cheated%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sunflowers'%20In%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20candidates%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20were%20with%20the%20BRS%20earlier%2C%20and%20Mr%20Rao%20had%20a%20quip%20reserved%20for%20them%3A%20%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20went%20out%20of%20the%20party...%20In%20politics%2C%20it%20is%20common%20that%20whenever%20power%20shifts%2C%20there%20are%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20sunflowers%20in%20each%20party...%20they%20will%20turn%20towards%20the%20sun%20and%20leave%20the%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20won%204%20seats%20in%20Telangana%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections%20and%20the%20party%20has%20claimed%20that%20it%20will%20enter%20the%20double%20digits%20in%20the%20state%20this%20time.%20When%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20comment%20on%20this%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20running%20a%20Goebbels%20campaign.%20The%20BJP%20will%20get%20only%20one%20or%20none%20in%20Telangana%20in%20these%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20chief%20minister%20asserted%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20won%20only%2029%20seats%20out%20of%20130%20(including%20Puducherry)%20in%20south%20India%20in%202019%2C%20would%20not%20win%20more%20than%2010%20this%20time%2C%20and%20that%20the%20NDA%20would%20be%20reduced%20to%20just%20226%20seats%20nationally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20lost%20his%20charisma.%20People%20have%20realised%20it.%20The%20value%20of%20the%20Rupee%20has%20gone%20down%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20and%20there%20is%20a%20capital%20drain%20from%20India%20now.%20Farmers%20are%20angry%2C%20many%20others%20are%20angry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EK%20Kavitha%20Arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20arrest%20of%20his%20daughter%20and%20BRS%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20on%20March%2015%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20said%20the%20BJP%20had%20done%20that%20because%20he%20had%20taken%20action%20against%20people%20who%20were%20trying%20to%20topple%20his%20government%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20a%20case%20filed%20against%20BJP%20National%20General%20Secretary%20BL%20Santhosh%20for%20allegedly%20poaching%20BRS%20MLAs%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20first%20chief%20Minister%20in%20India%20who%20vehemently%20opposed%20Mr%20Modi%20and%20many%20of%20his%20policies...%20I%20sent%20my%20police%20forces%20to%20the%20central%20office%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Delhi%20to%20catch%20BL%20Santhosh.%20That%20angered%20the%20BJP.%20That's%20why%20they%20arrested%20Kavitha%20in%20a%20false%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20judiciary.%20Today%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20got%20bail%2C%20I%20think%20my%20daughter%20will%20also%20get%20bail.%20The%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20is%20not%20a%20scam.%20Every%20state%20has%20a%20liquor%20policy...%20not%20a%20single%20rupee%20was%20recovered...%20they%20are%20playing%20a%20drama%20with%20my%20daughter%20and%20also%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20In%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20son%20and%20former%20minister%20KT%20Rama%20Rao's%20statement%20that%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20would%20switch%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20KCR%20said%20this%20was%20evident%20in%20how%20he%20had%20called%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20his%20big%20brother%20at%20an%20event%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20said%20we%20need%20your%20(PM%20Modi's)%20support%20going%20forward%20as%20well.%20What%20does%20it%20mean%3F%20He%20is%20accepting%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20not%20become%20Prime%20Minister.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20is%20in%20trouble%2C%20he%20is%20facing%20the%20(2015)%20vote-for-note%20case%20and%20I%20think%20that%20is%20coming%20to%20an%20end%20in%20June%20or%20July.%20Even%20people%20from%20the%20Congress%20are%20thinking%20he%20may%20jump%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20denied%20allegations%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20phone-tapping%20scandal%20that%20has%20rocked%20the%20state%20and%20said%20it%20was%20completely%20in%20the%20police's%20domain.%20He%20also%20called%20the%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20Kaleshwaram%20lift%20irrigation%20project%20%26quot%3Bsenseless%26quot%3B%20and%20termed%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bmarvel%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20PM%20saying%20that%20reservation%20to%20Muslims%20based%20on%20religion%20is%20not%20allowed%20under%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhether%20the%20Constitution%20allows%20it%20is%20an%20academic%20subject.%20But%20as%20far%20as%20I'm%20concerned%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20Muslim%20or%20Hindu%20or%20whatever%2C%20people%20who%20did%20not%20get%20their%20share%2C%20people%20who%20are%20still%20poor%2C%20who%20deserve%20reservation%2C%20must%20get%20reservation.%20It's%20not%20a%20fair%20thing%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India...%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20talking%20about%20it..%20it%20looks%20very%20silly.%20It's%20not%20correct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715368320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1865051_kcr_625x300_11_M