2%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashish%20on%20working%20with%20R%20Madhavan-Ajay%20in%20Shaitaan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715365423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110019160%2Cimgsize-14902.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fashish-gokhale-on-working-with-r-madhavan-and-ajay-devgn-in-shaitaan-they-both-have-treated-me-like-their-younger-brother-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F110019151.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110019151.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAshish%20Gokhale%2C%20a%20doctor-actor%2C%20shared%20his%20journey%20of%20balancing%20medical%20practice%20with%20acting.%20He%20discussed%20working%20with%20Ajay%20Devgn%20and%20R%20Madhavan%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20importance%20of%20education%20and%20hard%20work%20for%20aspiring%20actors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fashish-gokhale-on-working-with-r-madhavan-and-ajay-devgn-in-shaitaan-they-both-have-treated-me-like-their-younger-brother-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F110019151.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Airports%20Body%20Denying%20Maternity%20Leave%20To%20Employee%2C%20High%20Court%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBecoming%20a%20mother%20is%20a%20natural%20phenomenon%2C%20and%20an%20employer%20has%20to%20be%20considerate%20and%20sympathetic%20towards%20women%20staffers%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20while%20cancelling%20a%20communication%20issued%20by%20the%20Airport%20Authority%20of%20India%20(AAI)%20denying%20maternity%20leave%20to%20an%20employee%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20she%20already%20had%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20AS%20Chandurkar%20and%20Jitendra%20Jain%20said%20women%20who%20constitute%20almost%20half%20of%20the%20segment%20of%20our%20society%20have%20to%20be%20honoured%20and%20treated%20with%20dignity%20at%20places%20where%20they%20work%20to%20earn%20their%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20duties%2C%20vocation%20and%20workplace%2C%20women%20must%20be%20provided%20all%20the%20facilities%20to%20which%20they%20are%20entitled%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20quashed%20a%202014%20communication%20issued%20by%20the%20AAI%2C%20Western%20Region%20Headquarters%2C%20which%20refused%20maternity%20leave%20to%20an%20employee%2C%20citing%20that%20she%20already%20had%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20become%20a%20mother%20is%20the%20most%20natural%20phenomenon%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20woman.%20Whatever%20is%20needed%20to%20facilitate%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20child%20to%20a%20woman%20who%20is%20in%20service%2C%20the%20employer%20has%20to%20be%20considerate%20and%20sympathetic%20towards%20her%20and%20must%20realise%20the%20physical%20difficulties%20which%20a%20working%20woman%20would%20face%20in%20performing%20her%20duties%20at%20the%20workplace%20while%20carrying%20a%20baby%20in%20the%20womb%20or%20while%20rearing%20up%20the%20child%20after%20birth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20passed%20its%20judgment%20on%20petitions%20filed%20by%20the%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20Workers%20Union%20and%20Kanakavali%20Raja%20Armugam%20alias%20Kanakavali%20Shyam%20Sandal%2C%20challenging%20two%20communications%20issued%20by%20the%20AAI%2C%20Western%20Region%20Headquarters%20in%202014%20rejecting%20Kanakavali's%20application%20for%20maternity%20leave%20benefit%20as%20she%20already%20had%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20communications%20stated%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20ineligible%20for%20maternity%20leave%20as%20per%20the%20AAI%20Leave%20Regulations%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20first%20married%20to%20Raja%20Armugam%2C%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20AAI%2C%20and%20after%20his%20death%2C%20she%20was%20given%20a%20job%20on%20compassionate%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%2C%20in%20her%20plea%2C%20said%20she%20had%20one%20child%20from%20her%20previous%20marriage%2C%20and%20after%20her%20first%20husband's%20death%2C%20she%20remarried%2C%20and%20two%20children%20were%20born%20from%20the%20wedlock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20had%20not%20availed%20of%20maternity%20leave%20during%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20first%20child%20from%20her%20first%20marriage%20and%20had%20sought%20the%20benefit%20for%20the%20third%20childbirth%2C%20which%20the%20AAI%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20child%20was%20born%20in%202009%20in%20the%20interim%20before%20she%20got%20appointed%20on%20compassionate%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAI%20said%20under%20the%20Maternity%20Leave%20Regulations%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20Kanakavali%20already%20had%20two%20surviving%20children%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20third%20childbirth%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20she%20was%20not%20eligible%20for%20maternity%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20Article%2042%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20provides%20that%20the%20State%20shall%20make%20provision%20for%20securing%20just%20and%20human%20conditions%20of%20work%20and%20maternity%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2042%20speaks%20of%20%26quot%3Bjust%20and%20humane%20conditions%20of%20work%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmaternity%20relief%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right%20to%20reproduction%20and%20childrearing%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20an%20important%20facet%20of%20a%20person's%20right%20to%20privacy%2C%20dignity%20and%20bodily%20integrity%20under%20Article%2021.%20Article%2042%20enjoins%20the%20State%20to%20make%20provisions%20for%20securing%20just%20and%20humane%20work%20conditions%20and%20maternity%20relief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20as%20per%20the%20AAI's%20Maternity%20Leave%20Regulations%2C%20a%20woman%20employee%20can%20avail%20of%20maternity%20leave%20twice%20in%20her%20service%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20objective%20of%20this%20Regulation%20is%20to%20give%20maternity%20leave%20benefits%20and%20not%20to%20curb%20the%20population.%20The%20condition%20of%20two%20surviving%20children%20is%20subjected%20so%20that%20the%20maximum%20times%20a%20female%20employee%20can%20benefit%20is%20only%20twice.%20This%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20organisation%20is%20not%20without%20the%20services%20of%20the%20employee%20for%20more%20than%20two%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20since%20the%20petitioner%20had%20not%20availed%20the%20maternity%20leave%20benefit%20when%20she%20had%20her%20first%20child%2C%20she%20was%20eligible%20for%20the%20benefit%20when%20she%20had%20her%20third%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20benefit%20of%20maternity%20leave%20and%20the%20conditions%20imposed%20were%20drafted%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20normal%20circumstances%2C%20where%20a%20female%20employee%20marries%20only%20once%20and%20gives%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20regulations%20should%20be%20interpreted%20liberally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20role%20of%20the%20court%20is%20to%20understand%20the%20purpose%20of%20law%20in%20society%20and%20help%20the%20law%20achieve%20its%20purpose.%20When%20social%20reality%20changes%2C%20the%20law%20must%20change%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20Maternity%20Leave%20Benefits%20Regulation%20is%20to%20offer%20protection%20to%20a%20woman%2C%20and%20its%20importance%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20point%20of%20a%20woman%20employee's%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co