%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20claimed%20that%20the%20narrative%20that%20%26quot%3Bminority%20is%20in%20danger%26quot%3B%20is%20false%20and%20has%20been%20exposed%20while%20highlighting%20the%20report%20published%20by%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20PM%20(EAC-PM).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.republicworld.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024%2Fpm-modi-exclusive-interview-with-arnab-goswami-republic-on-nation-wants-to-know-live-updates%2F%3Famp%3D1%5C%22%3ERepublic%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20perception%20that%20has%20been%20created%20is%20%26quot%3Bproving%20to%20be%20a%20mistake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBetween%201950%20and%202015%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Hindus%20in%20India%20has%20decreased%20by%20about%208%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20that%20of%20minorities%20has%20increased%20by%2043%20per%20cent.%20The%20perception%20that%20has%20been%20created%20is%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20mistake.%20The%20wrong%20narrative%20is%20being%20exposed.%20Whatever%20meaning%20one%20has%20to%20take%20out%20of%20it%2C%20they%20can.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20bring%20out%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20Republic%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20factual%2C%20then%20the%20perceptions%20created%20as%20in%20that%20minority%20is%20being%20suppressed%20in%20India%2C%20there%20is%20no%20voice%20for%20the%20minority%20in%20India...%20all%20these%20narratives%20that%20are%20being%20created%2C%20all%20this%20allegation%20against%20India%2C%20please%20accept%20the%20truth%20and%20come%20out%20of%20this%20narrative%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBharat%20sarwajan%20hitaye%2C%20sarwajan%20sughaye%2C%20Vasudeva%20Kutumbakam%20bhavanayein%20ko%20lekar%20chalne%20wala%20desh%20hei%26quot%3B%20(India%20moves%20forward%20taking%20everyone's%20needs%20and%20wellness%20and%20ideas%20of%20'Vasudaiva%20Kutumbakam'%20into%20consideration)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20remarks%20after%20EAC-PM%20published%20a%20report%20that%20stated%20that%20in%20India%2C%20the%20share%20of%20the%20majority%20Hindu%20population%20decreased%20by%207.82%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015%20(from%2084.68%20per%20cent%20to%2078.06%20per%20cent)%2C%20while%20the%20share%20of%20the%20Muslim%20population%2C%20which%20in%201950%20was%209.84%20per%20cent%2C%20increased%20to%2014.09%20per%20cent%20in%202015--a%2043.15%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20their%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20EAC%20report%2C%20the%20share%20of%20the%20Christian%20population%20rose%20from%202.24%20per%20cent%20to%202.36%20per%20cent--an%20increase%20of%205.38%20per%20cent%20between%201950%20and%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20the%20Sikh%20population%20increased%20from%201.24%20per%20cent%20in%201950%20to%201.85%20per%20cent%20in%202015--a%206.58%20per%20cent%20rise%20in%20their%20share.%20Even%20the%20share%20of%20the%20Buddhist%20population%20witnessed%20a%20noticeable%20increase%20from%200.05%20per%20cent%20in%201950%20to%200.81%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Jains%20in%20the%20population%20of%20India%20decreased%20from%200.45%20per%20cent%20in%201950%20to%200.36%20per%20cent%20in%202015.%20The%20share%20of%20the%20Parsi%20population%20in%20India%20witnessed%20a%20stark%2085%20per%20cent%20decline%2C%20reducing%20from%200.03%20per%20cent%20share%20in%201950%20to%200.004%20per%20cent%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20take%20India%20forward.%20And%20the%20mantra%20I%20carry%20with%20me%20is%20Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'.%20When%20I%20started%20my%20work%20in%202014%2C%20I%20added%20one%20more%20to%20it%20Sabka%20Vishwas%20and%20also%20Sabka%20Prayas.%20There%20shouldn't%20be%20any%20discrimination%20in%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20government.%20Be%20it%20caste%2C%20gender%20or%20religion%20there%20shouldn't%20be%20any%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReservation%20based%20on%20religion%20is%20the%20most%20dangerous%20thing.%20No%20country%20can%20be%20run%20in%20that%20way.%20What%20happens%20is%20when%20I%20say%20Muslim%2C%20then%20the%20whole%20ecosystem%20around%20me%20says%20that%20Modi%20has%20mentioned%20Hindu-Muslim%20in%20the%20elections.%20Modi%20didn't%20bring%20Hindu-Muslim%2C%20it's%20in%20your%20actions%20that%20I%20need%20to%20expose%20you%20before%20the%20country.%20I%20must%20educate%20the%20people.%20If%20someone%20alleges%20me%20or%20points%20out%20my%20speech%2C%20neither%20have%20I%20spoken%20anything%20against%20Muslims%20or%20Islam.%20I'm%20speaking%20against%20the%20efforts%20to%20destroy%20the%20country%20in%20the%20name%20of%20secularism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715360220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fe5cbg57g_pm-modi_625x300_07_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrong-narrative-exposed-pm-modi-on-panels-findings-on-minorities-5635248%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20claimed%20that%20the%20narrative%20that%20%26quot%3Bminority%20is%20in%20danger%26quot%3B%20is%20false%20and%20has%20been%20exposed%20while%20highlighting%20the%20report%20published%20by%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20PM%20(EAC-PM).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwrong-narrative-exposed-pm-modi-on-panels-findings-on-minorities-5635248%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2F