d%20karate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuin%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20how%20a%20student%20is%20assigned%20a%20particular%20lever%20and%20how%20they%20navigate%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20joins%20Pathshala%2C%20we%20assess%20their%20current%20knowledge%20and%20comprehension%20abilities%20in%20languages%20and%20mathematics.%20Based%20on%20this%20evaluation%2C%20we%20place%20them%20in%20appropriate%20levels%20corresponding%20to%20their%20proficiency.%20Consequently%2C%20each%20child%20studies%20at%20different%20levels%20for%20various%20subjects.%20Upon%20completion%20of%20Level%205%2C%20a%20student%20becomes%20equivalent%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20sit%20for%20Class%208%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Class%208%20to%2012%2C%20the%20school%20adheres%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS)%20syllabus%2C%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20take%20psychometric%20tests%20to%20discover%20their%20career%20inclinations%2C%20guiding%20their%20subject%20choices%20when%20they%20enter%20Class%208.%20This%20personalised%20method%20ensures%20their%20interests%20and%20strengths%20are%20considered.%20Alongside%20languages%20and%20math%2C%20students%20explore%20diverse%20subjects%20through%20practical%20experiences%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20recently%2C%20the%20students%20completed%20a%20board%20game%20project%20where%20they%20designed%20and%20created%20their%20own%20board%20games%2C%20complete%20with%20unique%20rules.%20Students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20delve%20deeply%20into%20subjects%20of%20their%20choosing%20and%20conduct%20in-depth%20studies%20according%20to%20their%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children's%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmeen%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20living%20in%20Pathshala%20hostel%20and%20has%20been%20with%20Juin%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20shares%20his%20perspective%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20enriching%20aspect%20of%20our%20education%20is%20a%20class%20where%20we%20learn%20without%20textbooks.%20We%20select%20a%20topic%2C%20discuss%20it%2C%20and%20learn%20from%20each%20other%20and%20our%20teachers.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20educators%20stress%20on%20understanding%20concepts%20deeply%20rather%20than%20just%20memorisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20second%20chance%20at%20life%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20these%20kids%20have%20a%20safe%20place%20here%20to%20thrive%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20their%20lives%20still%20lingers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jui.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20hail%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20travel%20frequently