%20to%20almond%20or%20oats%20milk%20be%3F%E2%80%99%20they%20wondered.%20Prabu%20recalled%20his%20visit%20to%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20he%20had%20seen%20milk%20being%20extracted%20from%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20given%20to%20children.%20With%20this%20insight%2C%20they%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%20extract%20milk%20from%20millets%20and%20convert%20it%20into%20ice%20cream%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20thought%20led%20them%20to%20launch%20their%20hero%20product%20%E2%80%94%20millet%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20worked%20out%20of%20a%20300%20sqft%20space%20in%20Trichy%2C%20where%20they%20procured%20machines%20and%20started%20working%20on%20ways%20to%20extract%20milk%20from%20different%20millets.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20six%20months%2C%20they%20found%20that%20the%20major%20millets%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%2C%20bajra%2C%20ragi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20foxtail%20millet%20%E2%80%94%20produced%20good%20results.%20They%20then%20experimented%20with%20different%20sweeteners%20and%20fruits%2C%20and%20developed%20these%20ice-creams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20made-in-India%20vegan%20ice-cream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20six%20months%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20they%20finally%20started%20testing.%20They%20offered%20samples%20to%20neighbours%20and%20gated%20communities%20in%20Trichy.%20The%20overall%20feedback%20was%20positive%20with%20fresh%20fruit%20ice-creams%20emerging%20a%20clear%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1043tAKbEp%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1043tAKbEp%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2F