9CIt%20was%20a%20perfect%20place%20as%20it%20had%20ravine%20qualities%20and%20also%20a%20little%20elevation.%20I%20got%20down%20to%20drawing%20plans%20and%20making%20a%20budget.%20We%20formulated%20a%20project%20and%20presented%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20the%20forest%20departments%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Esecuring%20funding%20for%20its%20implementation.%20Following%20the%20funding%20acquisition%2C%20which%20was%20in%20March%202023%2C%20we%20started%20the%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20place%20has%20a%20plethora%20of%20activities%20including%20a%20trek%20and%20boating.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-8-1714748507-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349019%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20place%20has%20a%20plethora%20of%20activities%20including%20a%20trek%20and%20boating.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20was%20completed%20and%20opened%20to%20the%20public%20without%20a%20