area%2C%20and%20he%20also%20wanted%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20eco%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298606%2Fecosphere-encourages-sustainable-tourism-in-spiti-solar-power-homestays-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsible%20tourism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20to%20involve%20locals%20in%20the%20work.%20From%20helping%20with%20maintaining%20the%20forests%20to%20setting%20up%20such%20projects%20to%20rescuing%20wildlife%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20tradition%20for%20the%20department%20to%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20local%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20tradition%2C%20Vikas%20mapped%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20help%20the%20local%20community%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Guests%20can%20stay%20at%20the%20mud%20homes%20at%20the%20eco%20tourism%20centre.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ffarm-9-1714748560-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGuests%20can%20stay%20at%20the%20mud%